  <li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a href="http://ccb.jhu.edu/software/pebls/pebls.tar.gz" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(3, 101, 100); text-decoration: none; transition: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392);"><span class="s1" style="box-sizing: border-box;">The PEBLS memory-based reasoning system</span></a>.&nbsp; Originally developed by Scott Cost.</li>
